{"tid":1535341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠是我們的敵人，他們會以身體保護高牆","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T22:10:30.000Z","uid":134936,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec1a51c0ea1c8fb279a326238cb5707c14ecf41","tid":1535341,"uid":134936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:22:57.000Z","msg":"左膠只是以不同名義協助強權的打壓<br />\n左膠是我們的敵人<br />\n請不要忘記<br />\n左膠是站在高牆的一方<br />\n<br />\n左膠們<br />\n若你們清醒了<br />\n若你們想站在抗爭者的一方<br />\n請你們停止用身體保護高牆<br />\n請你們不要助紂為虐<br />\n若有餘下的，便是我們的敵人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠是我們的敵人"},{"pid":"a2f0e8e809bece5c957178858c5e11fdb7b6b195","tid":1535341,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:23:05.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d6f298e64998a34ed402471490f4c3bc2cc1d63","tid":1535341,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:23:29.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7d27367bd7cdee1c877f9f06ffb7ebc9e27a7211","tid":1535341,"uid":205482,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3neWRs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3neWRs.jpg&h=215fa50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1wLi4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1wLi4N.jpg&h=bba03645&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e9d1d2b475192fd495225330eb9ddb82e26171d","tid":1535341,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢成個訊息copy and paste嚟推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n額外事件：練美國歌國。事源 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"545f3445be310eda5909137efef8358b5c0fe67f","tid":1535341,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:55:19.000Z","msg":"推<del></del>"},{"pid":"286ca284ff04a6f79718a47458a6891d54ad2d1b","tid":1535341,"uid":216279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:08:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e69d2b853cde3a4ecc42b5c9c13fe883ea1a677","tid":1535341,"uid":292536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T22:09:56.000Z","msg":"講到口都臭，但係個個淨係掛住「不分化不割席不篤魁」就以為左膠係你哋嘅盟友。"